<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA102294-0143 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 091056 </DOCID>
<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
October 22, 1994, Saturday, Ventura West Edition 
</P>
