<HEADLINE>
<P>
SOUTHERN SECTION FOOTBALL ROUNDUP; MARMONTE LEAGUE 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By DAVID HARRIS 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Newbury Park 40, Channel Islands 0 -- Brock Diediker scored three touchdowns 
for host Newbury Park (4-3, 2-2).The Panthers racked up 361 yards, including a 
161-yard passing effort by Chris Czernek, who completed seven of 11, including 
a 30-yard touchdown to Diediker. 
</P>
<P>
 Tony Aceves and Garrett Hobba each scored on one-yard runs and reserve 
quarterback Justin Vint scored on a two-yard run. 
</P>
<P>
 Channel Islands (1-6, 0-4) had 71 total yards. Newbury Park, led by Ed 
Patterson, who returned an interception 32 yards, kept the Raiders from 
completing any of their 12 passes. DAVID HARRIS 
</P>
