<TEXT>
<P>
 The Los Angeles Jewish Symphony, directed by Noreen Green, will present "The 
Symphony Sings" concert Nov. 13 at 7:30 p.m. at Adat Ari El, 12020 Burbank 
Blvd., in North Hollywood. 
</P>
