<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
October 22, 1994, Saturday, Home Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Sports; Part C; Page 4; Column 1; Sports Desk 
</P>
</SECTION>
<LENGTH>
<P>
