<HEADLINE>
<P>
LOS ANGELES TIMES SPECIAL REPORT / BASEBALL; STAFF BOX 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Editor: Emillio Garcia-Ruiz 
</P>
<P>
 Design Editor: David F. Montesino 
</P>
<P>
 Copy Editors: Jerry Crowe, Steve Horn, Garr Kluender, Grahame L. Jones, Claire 
